snippet.title: God Eater 2: Rage Burst - Announcement Trailer | PS4, Vita, PC
snippet.description:
God Eater: Resurrection AND God Eater 2: Rage Burst are coming to the PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, and PC/Steam in the Americas!

Stay tuned for more information - 
God Eater on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/godeaterden 
God Eater on Twitter: https://twitter.com/godeaterden 
Official Game Site: http://www.god-eater.com/
